settings.name: RaShaun Brown
settings.bio: RaShaun is a sports professional from Westerville, Ohio. He graduated from Ohio University with degrees in sports management, business administration, marketing, and also received his masterâ€™s in sports administration from the Ohio University Sports Ad program. His professional background includes working with Russell Athletics, the Big East Conference, and the 12th Man Foundation - fundraising for Texas A&M Athletics.  He is the Founder of RMBrown Ventures, focusing on innovative digital sports platforms. His portfolio includes College Emojis, which he licensed to 2ThumbZ Ent. He also works with Sportsmanias to feed fans innovative AR/VR social content, which includes projects with the Collegiate Licensing Company, College Football Playoff and other brands.

settings.name: Clay Canning
settings.bio: Clay started his first business back in late 2017 as a side gig in High School. He later went on to design Screen Skinz shortly after and begin his journey to obtain licenses within the collegiate market. He obtained his first license with the Unviersity of South Florida in 2018. Sparking his journey to obtain licenses within the MLB, NBA, and NCAA. Clay is from Lakeland, FL and if there is one thing to know about him, he loves the day to day hustle!

settings.name: Nick Vannett
settings.bio: Nick is entering his 6th NFL season as a Tight End for the New Orleans Saints, he previosly played for the Seattle Seahawks, Pittsburgh Steelers and the Denver Broncos. He played college football at the Ohio State University, where he was the member of the 2014 National Championship Team. Nick is from Westerville, Ohio and Founder of NJV Sports LTD.

settings.heading: About Screen Skinz
settings.about_description: Based in Lakeland, Florida, we are a team of innovators that found a market we are passionate about and could make an impact through new product offerings. We combine our industry experience with a shared interest in sports and technology. We build screen protection for our customers to express themselves and PROTECT their phone screen with PASSION. We INNOVATE and COLLABORATE with our customers and brands in mind.
